id: pm-xh0y
title: Deduplicate mutation author fallback resolution across commands
description: "Duplicate audit 2026-05-22: mutation commands locally reimplement the same author fallback logic: explicit candidate, PM_AUTHOR, settings.author_default, trimmed value, then unknown fallback. Representative copies are resolveAuthor in src/cli/commands/append.ts:23, comments.ts:38, files.ts:108 and toAuthor in delete.ts:21 and history-redact.ts:111, with the same pattern also appearing in notes/learnings/docs/test/claim/close/update/restore/plan paths. Existing searches found only broad parent/history hits and adjacent command-stack items; no active item owns the shared mutation-author contract."
