acceptance_criteria: One shared helper owns mutation author resolution; command modules consume it without behavior changes; PM_AUTHOR/settings.author_default/unknown fallback semantics stay covered by focused command tests; pnpm build passes.
parent: pm-rnpb
resolution: Closed by extracting the shared mutation author resolver.
expected_result: "Mutation commands use one helper for explicit author, PM_AUTHOR, settings default, trim, and unknown fallback semantics."
actual_result: resolveAuthor was extracted to src/core/shared/author.ts and adopted across the mutation commands in PR #55.
